---
title: Golden Chicken Breast & Roasted Potatoes with Greek Salad & Mayo
description: We've put all the much-loved household flavours into this delectable dinner - from the golden-spiced chicken to the
roasted potatoes and refreshing Greek salad, it's got everything we're all addicted to!
